author: Special Correspondent
title: One patient dies, five more test positive in Kurnool
description: Testing begins on TrueNAT machines at four places in the district
content:
One COVID-19 positive person died and five new cases were reported since 11 am on Saturday taking the total number of cases to 129 in the district.
The number of dead has gone up to three. At various hospitals, 125 positive persons are still being treated. … [+2065 chars]
